products.name: 27" Single Electric Wall Oven
products.summary: The Frigidaire Gallery 27 in. Electric Wall Oven features a large 3.8 cu. ft. oven so you have more room to cook multiple items. Express-Select Control panel makes it easy to set cooking temperature at the touch of a button and the side swing door allows you to take dishes out of the oven with ease. True Convection features a third element and a single fan to distribute heat throughout the oven for faster and more even multi-rack baking.
